<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #F5F7FA;
            padding: 32px;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }

        span {
            color: #6366F1;
        }

        .link {
            color: #6366F1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        ul {
            line-height: 32px;
        }

        p,
        li {
            color: #46586B;
            font-family: 'SF Pro', sans-serif;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #46586B;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: 'SF Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'New York Large', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 32px;
        }

        main {
            background-color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 40px;
            gap: 40px;
            border-radius: 3px
        }

        .xertis-link {
            display: inline !important;
        }

        .xertis-link a {
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
        }

        .xertis-link p {
            color: #6366F1;
            font-family: 'SF Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: #6366F1;
            font-weight: 510;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .xertis-email-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        footer p {
            text-align: center;
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            body {
                padding: 16px;
            }

            main {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            footer {
                padding: 20px;
                align-items: start;
            }

            footer p {
                text-align: start;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main>
        <div class="xertis-link">
            <a href="client-link" target="_blank">
                <img src="./xertis-email-logo.svg" alt="Xertis logo" class="mb-1">
                <p>Xertis</p>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h1>Your Certificate Has Been Created Successfully!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="xertis-email-content">
            <p class="m-0">Hi {{username}},</p>
            <div>
                <p>
                    Your blockchain-powered certificate has been successfully created on Xertis!
                </p>
                <h3>Here's your minting link to share with recipients: <a
                        href="https://xertis-abc.vercel.app/{{mintId}}" target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer">https://xertis.vercel.app/claim/{{mintUrl}}</a></h3>
            </div>
            <h3>What's next?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Share the minting link with your recipients</li>
                <li>Recipients can log in, fill their details, and mint their certificates.</li>
            </ul>

            <div>
                <p class="m-0">
                    This certificate is secured on the blockchain, ensuring it’s tamper-proof and verifiable anytime,
                    anywhere.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p class="lh-base">Questions or concerns? Get in touch with us at <span>xertis.reply@gmail.com</span>
            <br>
            Never miss a beat! Follow us on <span>Twitter</span> , <span>Facebook</span> and <span>Instagram.</span>
        </p>
        <p>Don’t want any more emails from Xertis? <a href="https://xertis-abc.vercel.app" class="link"
                target="_blank">Unsubscribe.
            </a>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>